readable.content: A flock of birds disturbed and in flight in front of a wall that has a mural of three women and a man . A flock of birds flying past a chinese mural on a building . A flock of birds fly up from the ground next to a building with a mural . A group of birds fly up from the street against a painted wall . Flock of pigeons flying in front of building with a mural painted on it .
